#ROOMS
#8800
Walkway to Graviton High~
You stand atop a hill overlooking the bay that cradles 
Graviton city. Trees of green are lined across the cement 
walkway leading to Graviton High. Large groups of girls like 
gather here before school to gossip about things that seem 
vitally important to thier social lives.
~
