#8804
Entrance Hallway~
Gazing about, you notice a nice, orderly flight of stairs to 
the second level. Teachers patrol the hallways here, watching 
for girls who might lag behind thier other classmates on thier 
way. You get a feeling of order, and at the same time chaos, 
because of the strange events that keep occuring here.
